Package: lfcdata
Title: Access to the LFC Databases
Version: 0.0.6
Authors@R: person("Victor", "Granda", email = "victorgrandagarcia@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0469-1991"))
Description: Access the Spanish National Forest Inventory data for Catalonia, calculate
  tree and shrubs allometries or obtain rasters for eco-physiological variables based on
  LiDAR data. "lfcdata" allows retrieving data from all the available databases from
  the Catalonian Forest Laboratory (LFC) initiative
  (<http://laboratoriforestal.creaf.cat>). 
Depends: R (>= 3.6.0)
